OL,7,FThe decision not to make it a
OL,8,Frequirement for people to wear face
OL,9,Fcoverings in the first months of the
OL,10,Fpandemic was "confusing to the
OL,11,Fpublic", the Chief Medical Officer has
OL,12,Faccepted.
OL,14,FSir Frank Atherton, who was CMO
OL,15,Fthroughout the pandemic, has been
OL,16,Fgiving evidence at the UK Covid
OL,17,FInquiry hearings in Cardiff on Monday
OL,18,F(4 March).
