OL,7,FThe Welsh Government did not introduce
OL,8,Fthe mandatory wearing of a cloth face
OL,9,Fcovering until 9 June 2020, nearly a
OL,10,Fmonth after guidelines had been
OL,11,Fintroduced in England.
OL,13,FThe day after the decision was taken
OL,14,Fin England, Sir Frank published a
OL,15,Fstatement saying he thought it should
OL,16,Fbe a matter of personal choice, rather
OL,17,Fthan a rule.
