OL,7,FIn his evidence to the UK Covid
OL,8,Finquiry, Sir Frank said his advice was
OL,9,Fbased on three areas of concern.
OL,10,FFirstly, he said he was concerned
OL,11,Fabout the stock of PPE, given that the
OL,12,Fpriority was to ensure hospital and
OL,13,Fcare staff had access to face
OL,14,Fcoverings.
