OL,7,FHe told the inquiry his notepad was
OL,8,Fused to help him order his thoughts
OL,9,Fbefore he briefed ministers, and was
OL,10,Fjust a very informal means of record
OL,11,Fkeeping.
OL,13,F"Although I couldn't see a good
OL,14,Fargument for mandating, on a public
OL,15,Fhealth basis, the use of face
OL,16,Fcoverings as opposed to recommending,
OL,17,FI was clear with ministers that there
OL,18,Fwas a political choice to be made",
OL,19,FSir Frank told the inquiry.
