OL,7,F"It was extremely difficult", he
OL,8,Fcontinued.
OL,10,F"I felt as though I was putting
OL,11,Fministers in quite a difficult
OL,12,Fposition because I was taking a
OL,13,Fslightly different position to my
OL,14,Fother CMO colleagues (in England and
OL,15,FScotland) on this one.
