OL,7,FThe group repeated its call for the
OL,8,FWelsh specific Covid-19 Inquiry,
OL,9,Fsomething the Welsh Government has
OL,10,Frepeatedly rejected, saying scrutiny
OL,11,Fof interconnected-governmental
OL,12,Fdecisions can only be done on the UK-
OL,13,Fwide level.
OL,15,FEarlier in his evidence on Monday, Sir
OL,16,FFrank Atherton said he had "pretty
OL,17,Fmuch lost control" of his emails in
OL,18,Fthe early weeks of the pandemic when
OL,19,Fcases began to be identified in the UK.
