OL,7,F"I did feel like a bit of an outlier",
OL,8,Fhe told the inquiry in relation to the
OL,9,Famount of administrative support he
OL,10,Fwas getting in his role compared to
OL,11,Fthe CMOs of the other UK nations.
OL,13,FSir Frank said that due to the work by
OL,14,Fthe Welsh Government going into
OL,15,Fresponding to the floods in Wales in
OL,16,FFebruary 2020, he was not able to be
OL,17,Fgiven more resources in public health
OL,18,Fto respond to the growing threat from
OL,19,Fthe virus.
