OL,7,FThe CMO told the inquiry that the
OL,8,Fpandemic was "managed too long as a
OL,9,Fpurely health issue" partly, he said,
OL,10,Fbecause of the floods and the impacts
OL,11,Fof Brexit.
OL,13,FBy the middle of February, Sir Frank
OL,14,Fsaid he started to feel concerned that
OL,15,Fit was seen as a cross government
OL,16,Fissue.
OL,18,FAsked if he thought any action prior
OL,19,Fto the 23 March 2020 could have
OL,20,Favoided the need for a full national
OL,21,Flockdown, he said no.
